OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1780153874
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 14 Jun to Sun 28 Jun
OL,6,FDrier and more settled weather may
OL,7,Fdevelop as high pressure becomes more
OL,8,Fdominant, although some showery
OL,9,Finterludes are still possible. The
OL,10,Fforecast turns more mixed towards the
OL,11,Fend of the month, with rain and
OL,12,Fshowers perhaps having more of an
OL,13,Finfluence. Temperatures likely to
OL,14,Ftrend above average as we head further
OL,15,Finto June, with very warm spells
OL,16,Fpossible in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
